{"submitted": "2026-02-25T12:30:44.026-06:00", "type": "vendor_self", "region": "North America", "updated": "2026-02-25T12:30:44.329-06:00", "url": "https://www.g2.com/products/sage-intacct/reviews/12406281", "title": "Solid day-to-day accounting system for real estate accounting", "primary": "Americas", "switched_from": {"products": [{"id": "394", "name": "QuickBooks Online", "slug": "quickbooks-online"}], "reason": "We switched from QuickBooks to Sage Intacct because we’ve been growing and QuickBooks was starting to feel limiting for a multi-entity real estate business. Internally, we wanted cleaner records, stronger controls, and more consistent processes across AP, AR, cash, and month-end close.

Compared to QuickBooks, Intacct is better structured and easier to keep organized as volume increases. It’s much clearer to trace transactions and pull reporting without relying on as many manual spreadsheets. Overall it’s been a step up for day-to-day accounting efficiency and the quality of our financial records.

My work email is amy.chen@cedarcoast.com"}}

